{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/Fragments-low3434.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FRAGMENTS </h2></strong> is a captivating science fiction action-adventure role-playing game that designed and directed by Emrah Gonulkirmaz. The game intricately weaves together elements of puzzle-solving and survival. Players assume the role of a mnemonist[1] , embarking on a quest to recover fragments of their memories. In essence, Fragments can be characterized as a deliberately paced and enigmatic experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/HighresScreenshot00077-1.png?t=1710659811\" /><br><br><i>&quot;In the desolate expanse of a world forgotten by the winds, where humanity clung to the brutalist monoliths as their sanctuaries against the relentless assault of artificial weather, a man awoke. Void of memories, his mind was a blank slate, an empty vessel in a sea of chaos. This man, whom we shall call Eron, found himself in the midst of a journey not chosen but thrust upon him\u2014a quest for the fragments of his past.<br><br>This emptiness within him was a void no amount of data or recollections could fill, a chasm that seemed to stretch with his every step. Eron's journey for fragments of his past was as much about filling this void as it was about understanding his place in a world that had moved on without him. &quot;</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MNEMONIST THE PROTAGONIST </h2><br>\u201cFragments The Game\u201d set in a far future of an unknown place. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/75fb2217dd81c99b0cb90f696ac00623_original.png?t=1710659811\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/4f274db99010fff4e639c4ba72970530_original.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br>you can augment yourself to protect and survive<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/d2560fb14104e7366d5aa50f686dcbf6_original.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br>Hacking in to camera shows you what is beyond and gives you clues<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/ezgif-1-449ce2df00.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br>A-DOG is a friendly Ai which you can use for portable storage and can follow you. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/ezgif-1-bf7b760716.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br>Lidar Augmentation allows you to see interactable clues around you. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/ezgif-4-02765888d2.gif?t=1710659811\" /><br><br>Cinematic Cuts<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/extras/Screenshot_-_2022-10-21_19.34.37.jpg?t=1710659811\" /><br><br>In Fragments, knowledge emerges as the paramount asset. The dialogue system, acting as the narrative driver, stands as the key mechanism for unraveling the story and acquiring invaluable knowledge within the game.<br><br><br>//<br><br>Fragments undergoes continuous evolution, and your support is pivotal. If you appreciate the game, kindly add it to your Wishlist. I am actively developing an early build demo, aiming to provide you with an immersive gaming experience. Your feedback is invaluable, and I appreciate your anticipation<br><br>Thank you <br><br><br>\u25fc\ufe0f FRAGMENTS","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1710659811","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196060/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1710